# cytoscape-express 后端地址（BFF 层）
VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3000

# ========== 联调方式（二选一）==========
#
# 【MetaX mx17】express 跑本机，topo-server 在 mx17
#   1. SSH 隧道：ssh -L 4000:192.168.162.17:4000 -p 14735 yaowenxuan@metax-17-jump
#   2. express .env：SERVER_URL_BASE=127.0.0.1:4000  NEO4J_ENABLED=true
#   3. 本文件保持：VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3000
#   详见 https://github.com/theFly6/topo-server/blob/main/deploy/platforms/metax/README.md
#
# 【天津 tj-24】express 跑 tj-24，本机只跑前端
#   1. SSH 隧道：ssh -L 3000:127.0.0.1:3000 tj-24
#   2. 本文件保持：VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3000
#   详见 https://github.com/theFly6/topo-server/blob/main/deploy/tj/README.md
